title: Suns waive center Henry Sims, reduce roster to 14
text:
Phoenix Suns waive center Henry Sims, reducing roster to 14 THE ASSOCIATED PRESS   25, 2015 - 12:22 amLast Updated: October 25, 2015 - 12:23 am   
People: 

PHOENIX — The Phoenix Suns have waived center Henry Sims, reducing their roster to 14. 
The 6-foot-10 Sims signed with the Suns on Sept. 16. He appeared in all six Phoenix preseason games, scoring 10 points in 28 minutes. 
The Suns open their season Wednesday night at home against Dallas. 
The roster: 
Guards Eric Bledsoe, Brandon Knight, Devin Booker, Archie Goodwin, Ronnie Price 
Guard/Forward Sonny Weems 
Forwards Markieff Morris, P.J. Tucker, T.J. Warren, Cory Jefferson, Jon Leuer, Mirza Teletovic 
Centers Tyson Chandler, Alex Len
